00:04:51.880 --> 00:04:55.770
when in doubt, just don't. Avoid entering any

82
00:04:55.880 --> 00:04:59.430
personally identifiable student information into these systems.

83
00:05:00.060 --> 00:05:04.020
It is the single most effective way to protect your students and to

84
00:05:04.080 --> 00:05:07.980
protect yourself. All this talk about responsibility over student

